extendedInfo.description: Ever wished to have a study companion who can organize your studies? Now, Learn Faster, Revise Quicker & Remember Better with EduLanche Student!With AIPGMEE (NEET-PG), AIIMS questions ready for quick revision & DNB questions soon to be included this is the ideal tool for Medical PG Entrance preparation. NB: EduLanche Student is a PAID APP. Visit http://www.edulanche.com/mobile to subscribe. Features* Pricing: INR 3/day i.e., Rs. 555 for 6 months.  (Last updated: 5 August, 2013)* After single time installation, EduLanche Student App runs without a Net connection. Enjoy the freedom.* With 9000 MCQ's from AIPGMEE & AIIMS MD/MS 2001-2012, this is probably the largest MCQ app in the store!* Year wise & Subject wise listing of questions for convenience* 'Learning mode' & 'Exam mode' for a customised learning experience* Know your scores in real time and evaluate your performance in comparison to peers* Surprises? Yes, As it happens with EduLanche products, there will be more features inside than we list out here.How to activate EduLanche Student subscription?1. Create an account on EduLanche.com: This is required to receive one-time username & password. Already have one? Sign in to edulanche.com with the username & password.2. Subscribe to Mobile plans: Visit EduLanche store (www.edulanche.com/buy) and choose your plan & period. Proceed to checkout where you can make the payment. All payment modes including Credit/Debit cards or Net banking supported. 3. It's done! Sign in to the App: Users who have successfully subscribed can now sign in to the mobile app with username & password received in Step 1. Please note,* ES makes learning & revising MCQ's more fun and faster. The app is not designed to replace text book reading.* Explanations are being added by our expert panel and NOT ALL MCQ's have explanations as of now.* The Question view pages are function rich and may appear slow/force close if you have many apps running in the device at the same time. * We recommend users to switch off background music (in 'Settings') in case you experience speed issues on devices with low processor capacities.Roadmap* DNB questions to be available in version 1.2 to be released in October, 2013.* EduLanche store coupons available from medical book stores soon. (http://edulanche.com/updates/9849)---Useful links---Web pagehttp://www.edulanche.com/mobileEduLanche Storehttp://www.edulanche.com/buyFAQ'shttp://www.edulanche.com/faq/mobileFor suggestions please write to EduLanche Mobile at, mail@edulanche.com.
